attributes.action: Force an election due to no confidence in Kier Starmer or the Labour Government.
attributes.additional_details: I want our MPs to understand the true mindset of the British public and how after the budget and how the Labour Party has gone against it's manifesto, the reason they were voted in. Kier Starmer has no clue what the UK wants or needs.
attributes.background: We need an early general election.

rejection.details:
You may wish to sign the following petition, which calls for similar action:

Dissolve Parliament and call a General Election now!
https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/750050
